{"about_the_game":"Struggling with digital addiction? Need better self-control and fewer distractions? Let Focus Plant assist you!<br><br><strong>Focus Plant is a gamified focus timer</strong> designed to help you manage your time and concentrate on the important things in life. When self-discipline isn't enough to keep you off your distractions, gamification steps in. <br><br>Transform barren landscapes by turning your focus time into raindrops and growing adorable plants. These magical plants will help you manage your time and stay focused on what truly matters.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Stay focused</h2>Beat digital addiction and stay In control.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150410/extras/ScreenShot_Steam_06.png?t=1723904002\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Nurture plants</h2>Use your focus minutes to discover and grow adorable plants.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150410/extras/ScreenShot_Steam_01.png?t=1723904002\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Multiple focus modes</h2>Choose from Pomodoro timer, stopwatch timer, countdown timer, or group focus.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150410/extras/ScreenShot_Steam_03.png?t=1723904002\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Detailed reports</h2>Track your focus time to better plan your tasks.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150410/extras/ScreenShot_Steam_14.png?t=1723904002\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Play with friends</h2>Focus with your friends and reach your goals.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150410/extras/ScreenShot_Steam_13.png?t=1723904002\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Decorate</h2>Attract visitors and decorate your garden.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/app